Package com.example.proyectoFinal.controller

Class ObjectController

java.lang.Object
com.example.proyectoFinal.controller.ObjectController
@CrossOrigin(origins="*") @RestController @RequestMapping("/api/items") public class ObjectController extends Object
Controller responsible for handling operations related to game objects (items). Provides endpoints for creating, retrieving, updating, and deleting items.
